Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:07.41,正文,,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧 外甥\N{\fs16}If I may, nephew,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:10.01,正文,,0,0,0,,想当初我和一个副官在石磨坊打仗\N{\fs16}I encountered a situation with one of my lieutenants{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:12.25,正文,,0,0,0,,那可是场――\N{\fs16}at the Stone Mill which may have some bearing--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.58,正文,,0,0,0,,你怎么还要提那该死的石磨坊？\N{\fs16}Why don't you shut your mouth about that damned mill?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:18.45,正文,,0,0,0,,还有你别叫他“外甥” 他是你的国王\N{\fs16}And don't call him "nephew." He is your king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.49,0:04:19.92,正文,,0,0,0,,罗柏知道我并非有意对他不敬――\N{\fs16}Robb knows I meant him no disr--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:23.46,正文,,0,0,0,,我不是你的国王真算你走运\N{\fs16}You're lucky I'm not your king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:25.66,正文,,0,0,0,,我不会允许你把自己的蠢行\N{\fs16}I wouldn't let you wave your blunders around{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.20,正文,,0,0,0,,当成胜利四处宣扬\N{\fs16}like a victory flag.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.83,正文,,0,0,0,,是我的蠢行让泰温的疯狗\N{\fs16}My blunder sent Tywin's mad dog{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:33.00,正文,,0,0,0,,夹着尾巴逃回了凯岩城\N{\fs16}scurrying back to Casterly Rock with his tail between his legs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:35.17,正文,,0,0,0,,我想罗柏国王明白 光他一个人打胜仗\N{\fs16}I think King Robb understands we're not gonna win this war{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:36.84,正文,,0,0,0,,我们是赢不了这场战争的\N{\fs16}if he's the only one winning any battles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.35,正文,,0,0,0,,所以 这场胜利的荣耀足够我宣扬了吧\N{\fs16}No, there's glory enough to go around.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.24,正文,,0,0,0,,这与荣耀无关\N{\fs16}It's not about glory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.68,正文,,0,0,0,,你收到的指令是等他主动出击\N{\fs16}Your instructions were to wait for him to come to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.15,正文,,0,0,0,,可我抓住了一个机会\N{\fs16}I seized an opportunity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.08,正文,,0,0,0,,那这磨坊有什么价值吗？\N{\fs16}What value was the mill?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.32,正文,,0,0,0,,魔山想要从那过河\N{\fs16}The Mountain was garrisoned across the river from it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.69,正文,,0,0,0,,那他现在在那儿？\N{\fs16}Is he there now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.92,正文,,0,0,0,,当然不在 我们拦截了他\N{\fs16}Of course not. We took the fight to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.96,0:04:55.19,正文,,0,0,0,,他打不过我们\N{\fs16}He could not withstand us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.23,0:04:58.43,正文,,0,0,0,,我本想诱敌西入\N{\fs16}I wanted to draw the Mountain into the west,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:02.66,正文,,0,0,0,,在我们的地盘上 就可以趁机剿灭他\N{\fs16}into our country where we could surround him and kill him{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:04.80,正文,,0,0,0,,我故意让他追赶我们\N{\fs16}I wanted him to chase us,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:08.30,正文,,0,0,0,,他会这么做的\N{\fs16}which he would have done because he is a mad dog{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.54,正文,,0,0,0,,因为他就是一条没脑子的疯狗\N{\fs16}without a strategic thought in his head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:13.58,正文,,0,0,0,,我原本可以把他的脑袋插到木桩上\N{\fs16}I could have that head on a spike by now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.45,正文,,0,0,0,,可是我现在只有个磨坊\N{\fs16}Instead, I have a mill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.85,正文,,0,0,0,,我们有人质\N{\fs16}We took hostages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:26.59,正文,,0,0,0,,威廉・兰尼斯特 马丁・兰尼斯特\N{\fs16}Willem Lannister. Martyn Lannister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:29.13,正文,,0,0,0,,他们两个才14岁\N{\fs16}Willem and Martyn Lannister are 14 years old.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:31.59,正文,,0,0,0,,我想马丁是15岁\N{\fs16}Martyn is 15, I believe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.97,0:05:39.00,正文,,0,0,0,,我的两个妹妹在泰温・兰尼斯特手上\N{\fs16}Tywin Lannister has my sisters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.97,正文,,0,0,0,,我有求和吗？\N{\fs16}Have I sued for peace?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:42.51,正文,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs16}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.94,正文,,0,0,0,,那你认为他会\N{\fs16}Do you think he'll sue for peace{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:47.08,正文,,0,0,0,,因为他父亲的\N{\fs16}because we have his father's{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:49.98,正文,,0,0,0,,兄弟的重孙子来求和吗？\N{\fs16}brother's great-grandsons?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.69,0:05:56.15,正文,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs16}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.19,正文,,0,0,0,,你们损失了多少人？\N{\fs16}How many men did you lose?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.92,正文,,0,0,0,,208\N{\fs16}208.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:03.23,正文,,0,0,0,,可是我们每战死一人 兰尼斯特就――\N{\fs16}But for every man we lost, the Lannisters--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.26,0:06:06.20,正文,,0,0,0,,我们比泰温更缺人！\N{\fs16}We need our men more than Tywin needs his!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:14.34,正文,,0,0,0,,抱歉\N{\fs16}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:16.74,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我不知道 - 你本该知道\N{\fs16}- I didn't know. - You would have.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:20.01,正文,,0,0,0,,要是刚才我们交流时你能给点耐心\N{\fs16}Right here today at this gathering if you had been patient.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:23.35,正文,,0,0,0,,看起来这里可没几个人有耐心了\N{\fs16}We seem to be running short of patience here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.38,0:06:25.82,正文,,0,0,0,,你们知道谁有耐心么？\N{\fs16}You know who isn't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.09,正文,,0,0,0,,泰温・兰尼斯特\N{\fs16}Tywin Lannister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.40,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(521.778,226.96)}{\pos(200,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}培提尔・贝里席{\b0}\N{\fs12}  “小指头” 财政大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.40,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(339.556,229.619)}{\pos(400,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}瓦里斯{\b0}\N{\fs12} “八爪蜘蛛” 情报总管
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:45.40,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(111.778,226.832)}{\pos(390,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}派席尔{\b0}\N{\fs12}大学士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.80,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(291.362,200.647)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}提利昂・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“小恶魔”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:52.60,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(159.556,187.594)}{\pos(380,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}泰温・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}凯岩城公爵 国王之手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:20.00,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(193.929,226.078)}{\pos(320,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}瑟曦・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}摄政太后
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:23.54,正文,,0,0,0,,这桌子可真贴心可爱\N{\fs16}Intimate. Lovely table.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:26.37,正文,,0,0,0,,椅子也比小议会厅的好\N{\fs16}Better chairs than the old small council chamber.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:29.84,正文,,0,0,0,,跟共事的大臣们也真够近 这我喜欢\N{\fs16}Conveniently close to your own quarters. I like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:32.71,正文,,0,0,0,,有詹姆的消息了吗？\N{\fs16}What news of Jaime?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.99,正文,,0,0,0,,2万低贱的北方人\N{\fs16}20,000 unwashed Northerners{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.05,正文,,0,0,0,,都知道他已经失踪了好几周了\N{\fs16}have known about his escape for weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.09,0:08:43.46,正文,,0,0,0,,总体来说 我们掌握的密探和信息\N{\fs16}Collectively, you control more spies and informants{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.39,正文,,0,0,0,,比其他所有人都多\N{\fs16}than the rest of the world combined.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:47.33,正文,,0,0,0,,你们是想告诉我 你们当中没有一个人\N{\fs16}Do you mean to tell me that none of you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.46,正文,,0,0,0,,知道他在哪里吗？\N{\fs16}has any notion of where he is?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.47,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我们正在尽力 大人  - 那就尽全力\N{\fs16}- We are trying, my lord. - Try harder.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:56.74,正文,,0,0,0,,那目前我们知道什么？\N{\fs16}What do we have, then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:59.64,正文,,0,0,0,,罗柏・史塔克还有他大部分军队正在奔流城\N{\fs16}Robb Stark and most of his bannermen are in Riverrun{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:03.44,正文,,0,0,0,,给他外祖父霍斯特・徒利举办葬礼\N{\fs16}for the funeral of his grandfather Lord Hoster Tully.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:08.58,正文,,0,0,0,,史塔克不在的时候 赫伦堡由卢斯・波顿镇守\N{\fs16}In Stark's absence, Roose Bolton holds Harrenhal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:12.19,正文,,0,0,0,,这样一来 他就是事实上的赫伦堡公爵\N{\fs16}which would seem to make him Lord of Harrenhal,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.34,正文,,0,0,0,,- 只是少个头衔罢了  - 随便 让他占着吧\N{\fs16}- in practice if not in name. - Well, let him have it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.35,0:09:16.22,正文,,0,0,0,,赫伦堡公爵的头衔\N{\fs16}The name suits our purposes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.26,正文,,0,0,0,,比起一堆废墟来说 对我们更有用\N{\fs16}far more than that useless pile of rubble.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.33,0:09:22.39,正文,,0,0,0,,赫伦堡公爵将会是艾林家寡妇理想的配偶\N{\fs16}The Lord of Harrenhal will make a worthy suitor for the widow Arryn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:25.36,正文,,0,0,0,,对此我对您心怀感激 大人\N{\fs16}For which I am extremely grateful to you, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:28.00,正文,,0,0,0,,艾林夫人和我青梅竹马\N{\fs16}Lady Arryn and I have known each other since we were children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.50,正文,,0,0,0,,她总是……\N{\fs16}She has always been...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.07,正文,,0,0,0,,对我有好感\N{\fs16}positively predisposed toward me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.41,正文,,0,0,0,,如果求婚成功\N{\fs16}A successful courtship would make Lord Baelish{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.24,正文,,0,0,0,,贝里席大人将会成为谷地的主人\N{\fs16}acting Lord of the Vale.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:41.11,正文,,0,0,0,,一职生多职 倒是一点都不错\N{\fs16}Titles do seem to breed titles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:43.32,正文,,0,0,0,,你要前往艾林谷 越快越好\N{\fs16}You'll leave for the Eyrie as soon as possible{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.12,正文,,0,0,0,,把莱莎・艾林管住\N{\fs16}and bring Lysa Arryn into the fold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:48.15,正文,,0,0,0,,这样少狼主就要把自己的小阿姨给\N{\fs16}Then the young wolf can add his own aunt to the list{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.19,0:09:50.02,正文,,0,0,0,,列为敌人了\N{\fs16}of people who have taken up arms against him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.86,正文,,0,0,0,,我可无意于阻止真爱重逢啊\N{\fs16}Far be it from me to hinder true love,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:57.43,正文,,0,0,0,,不过贝里席大人的离开会带来一定的问题\N{\fs16}but Lord Baelish's absence would present certain problems.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:59.37,正文,,0,0,0,,国王的婚礼 这项空前浩大的盛事\N{\fs16}The royal wedding may end up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:02.27,正文,,0,0,0,,会因此夭折\N{\fs16}being the most expensive event in living memory.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.30,0:10:05.44,正文,,0,0,0,,夏天已经结束了 艰苦的日子还在前头呢\N{\fs16}Summer has ended, hard days lie ahead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:09.31,正文,,0,0,0,,现在把王室的财务搁置起来可不合适\N{\fs16}Not a good time to leave the crown's finances unattended.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.51,正文,,0,0,0,,完全赞同\N{\fs16}Fully agreed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.65,正文,,0,0,0,,所以我要命你担任新的财务大臣\N{\fs16}Which is why I'm naming you new Master of Coin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:16.58,正文,,0,0,0,,财务大臣？\N{\fs16}Master of Coin?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:19.25,正文,,0,0,0,,这将会是最适合你的位置\N{\fs16}It would appear to be a position that best suits your talents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.22,正文,,0,0,0,,花钱我倒是很会\N{\fs16}I'm quite good at spending money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.22,正文,,0,0,0,,虽然我这辈子都腰缠万贯\N{\fs16}but a lifetime of outrageous wealth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:24.96,正文,,0,0,0,,但没学会怎么理财\N{\fs16}hasn't taught me much about managing it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.99,0:10:28.63,正文,,0,0,0,,我一点都不怀疑你会证明自己能胜任这个挑战\N{\fs16}I have no doubt you will prove equal to this challenge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:30.36,正文,,0,0,0,,同意 同意\N{\fs16}Hear, hear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.64,正文,,0,0,0,,把她举在空中\N{\fs16}He lifted her high in the air{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.87,正文,,0,0,0,,他笑着喊着跟着香味在着弄\N{\fs16}He sniffed and roared and smelled her there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:38.24,正文,,0,0,0,,遍踢遍喊 少女惊恐\N{\fs16}She kicked and wailed, a maid so fair{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:40.84,正文,,0,0,0,,可他舔蜂蜜的发丛\N{\fs16}But he licked the honey from her hair{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:43.61,正文,,0,0,0,,这头儿 那儿弄\N{\fs16}From there to here, from here to there{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.65,0:10:45.75,正文,,0,0,0,,全身黑棕 罩着毛绒\N{\fs16}All black and brown and covered with hair{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.78,0:10:47.92,正文,,0,0,0,,他跟随夏日里的气涌\N{\fs16}He smelled that girl in the summer air{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.12,正文,,0,0,0,,狗熊 狗熊 少女美容\N{\fs16}The bear, the bear and the maiden fair...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.15,正文,,0,0,0,,这下你高兴啦\N{\fs16}I hope you're pleased.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:58.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(475.209,179.423)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}詹姆・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“弑君者” 御林铁卫队长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.19,0:10:56.66,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你当初给我武器 他们就不会把我们抓了\N{\fs16}If you had armed me, they never would have taken us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:58.66,正文,,0,0,0,,我们被抓的时候你不是带着武器么\N{\fs16}You were armed when we were taken.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.73,0:11:00.36,正文,,0,0,0,,你不记得我当时被锁起来了么\N{\fs16}I was in chains if you recall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.30,正文,,0,0,0,,要不是我的手被捆住了\N{\fs16}Our little match would have ended quite quick{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:06.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(307.963,225.005)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}布蕾妮・塔斯{\b0}\N{\fs12}\N“美人” 詹姆的保护者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:04.26,正文,,0,0,0,,我们的比试早就结束了\N{\fs16}if my hands weren't bound.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:07.60,正文,,0,0,0,,我从小到大都听到说\N{\fs16}All my life I've been hearing, "Jaime Lannister,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:10.30,正文,,0,0,0,,“詹姆・兰尼斯特是个多么杰出的剑客”\N{\fs16}what a brilliant swordsman."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:12.64,正文,,0,0,0,,你比我想象中要慢\N{\fs16}You were slower than I expected.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.67,0:11:14.41,正文,,0,0,0,,而且也没那么难以预测\N{\fs16}And more predictable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.01,正文,,0,0,0,,那是因为我在满是淤泥的牢笼里\N{\fs16}I've been sitting in a muddy pen{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:17.84,正文,,0,0,0,,被铁链锁了整整一年\N{\fs16}wrapped in chains for the past year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:19.81,正文,,0,0,0,,我可是个女人 照样把你给打败了\N{\fs16}And I'm a woman. I was still beating you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:22.28,正文,,0,0,0,,你可没有打败我\N{\fs16}You were not beating me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:24.48,正文,,0,0,0,,或许你是有像人们传说中那么厉害……\N{\fs16}Maybe you were as good as people said...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:26.59,正文,,0,0,0,,曾经是\N{\fs16}once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.62,0:11:29.69,正文,,0,0,0,,或许人们只是喜欢鼓吹有名气的人\N{\fs16}Or maybe people just love to overpraise a famous name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:36.16,正文,,0,0,0,,今晚我们扎营的时候 你就会被强奸\N{\fs16}When we make camp tonight, you'll be raped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.73,正文,,0,0,0,,还不止一次\N{\fs16}More than once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:40.94,正文,,0,0,0,,这些伙计可从没见过贵族女人\N{\fs16}None of these fellows have ever been with a noblewoman.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.17,0:11:44.84,正文,,0,0,0,,你最好别反抗\N{\fs16}You'd be wise not to resist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:46.94,正文,,0,0,0,,- 是吗？ - 他们会打断你的牙\N{\fs16}- Would I? - They'll knock your teeth out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.98,0:11:48.44,正文,,0,0,0,,你以为我会在乎自己的牙？\N{\fs16}You think I care about my teeth?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.71,正文,,0,0,0,,不 我不管你是不是在乎自己的牙齿\N{\fs16}No, I don't think you care about your teeth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:56.72,正文,,0,0,0,,如果反抗 他们会宰了你\N{\fs16}If you fight them, they will kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.45,正文,,0,0,0,,明白吗？\N{\fs16}Do you understand?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:12:01.22,正文,,0,0,0,,对他们有价值的犯人是我 而不是你\N{\fs16}I'm the prisoner of value, not you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:03.56,正文,,0,0,0,,他们要怎样就怎样好了 有什么要紧？\N{\fs16}Let them have what they want. What does it matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:05.79,正文,,0,0,0,,- 有什么要紧？ - 闭上你的眼睛\N{\fs16}- What does it matter? - Close your eyes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.63,正文,,0,0,0,,假装他们是蓝礼\N{\fs16}Pretend they're Renly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:11.67,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你是个女人 你就不会反抗？\N{\fs16}If you were a woman, you wouldn't resist?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.00,正文,,0,0,0,,你就会让他们蹂躏？\N{\fs16}You'd let them do what they wanted?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:17.04,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我是个女人 我就让他们杀了我\N{\fs16}If I was a woman, I'd make them kill me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:19.44,正文,,0,0,0,,幸亏我不是 感谢诸神\N{\fs16}But I'm not, thank the gods.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.08,0:12:26.08,正文,,0,0,0,,如果有像样的熔炉 我可以把它搞得跟新的一样\N{\fs16}If I had a proper forge, I could make it good as new.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(572.332,303.704)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}詹德利{\b0}\N{\fs12}“大牛” 铁匠学徒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:28.01,正文,,0,0,0,,没必要弄的多漂亮\N{\fs16}Doesn't have to look pretty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(101.857,233.43)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}密尔的索罗斯{\b0}\N{\fs12}无旗兄弟会的红袍僧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:30.45,正文,,0,0,0,,只要能挡掉射过来的箭就可以了\N{\fs16}It just has to keep the arrows out of my heart.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.48,0:12:32.62,正文,,0,0,0,,你为什么要帮他？\N{\fs16}Why are you helping him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.65,0:12:34.85,正文,,0,0,0,,他俘虏我们 现在又成了我们的朋友？\N{\fs16}He takes us prisoner and now he's our friend?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.89,0:12:36.49,正文,,0,0,0,,你可不是我的俘虏 小小姐\N{\fs16}You're not our prisoner, little lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.60,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(410.604,225.523)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}艾莉亚・史塔克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:38.66,正文,,0,0,0,,- 那我是什么？ - 我们的客人\N{\fs16}- What am I? - Our guest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.76,正文,,0,0,0,,没有人把你锁起来\N{\fs16}No one's put any chains on you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.53,正文,,0,0,0,,那我可以走了么？\N{\fs16}So I can walk away, then?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.37,正文,,0,0,0,,这片森林对奈德・史塔克的女儿来说可不安全\N{\fs16}These woods aren't safe for Ned Stark's daughter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:47.67,正文,,0,0,0,,被我们找到算你走运\N{\fs16}You're lucky we found you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:55.14,正文,,0,0,0,,你以为自己很会射箭嘛 小孬种？\N{\fs16}You think you're good with that bow, you little twat?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:12:56.74,正文,,0,0,0,,比你见过的任何人都要好\N{\fs16}Better than anyone you've ever met.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:58.71,正文,,0,0,0,,这是懦夫的武器\N{\fs16}A coward's weapon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.88,正文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢近身搏斗\N{\fs16}I like to fight up close.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.35,正文,,0,0,0,,我喜欢在我捅进别人身体的时候看着他的脸\N{\fs16}I like to see a man's face when I put the steel in him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(120.948,213.698)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}安盖{\b0}\N{\fs12}“射手” 来自风暴地的弓箭手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:06.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(346.726,212.812)}{\pos(180,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}桑铎・克里冈{\b0}\N{\fs12}“猎狗”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.72,正文,,0,0,0,,为什么？那你就可以吻他了？\N{\fs16}Why? So you can kiss him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.86,正文,,0,0,0,,你还记得上一次你在这儿的时候？\N{\fs16}You remember the last time you were here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.29,0:13:12.43,正文,,0,0,0,,跟路上遇到的破烂酒馆都一个样\N{\fs16}Looks like every other shit inn on the road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.06,正文,,0,0,0,,不好意思 但是你实在太他妈丑了\N{\fs16}Now, apologies, but you're one ugly fucker{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:17.30,正文,,0,0,0,,还是不要让我看见你的脸\N{\fs16}and I'd rather not see you no more.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.71,正文,,0,0,0,,悠着点啊\N{\fs16}Watch your head.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.14,正文,,0,0,0,,走咯\N{\fs16}Off we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:28.48,正文,,0,0,0,,出发！\N{\fs16}Walk up!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.28,0:13:34.58,正文,,0,0,0,,你干嘛呢？ 我们要走了\N{\fs16}What are you doing? We're about to leave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.08,正文,,0,0,0,,我要留在这\N{\fs16}I'm staying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:40.66,正文,,0,0,0,,什么？\N{\fs16}You're what?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.10,0:13:44.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(168.894,250.077)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}“热派”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.96,正文,,0,0,0,,我给酒馆老板烤了些黄面包\N{\fs16}I baked some brown bread for the innkeep{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.83,正文,,0,0,0,,她说这是她吃过最好的\N{\fs16}and she said she never had better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:46.73,正文,,0,0,0,,她告诉索罗斯要把我留下\N{\fs16}Told Thoros she's keeping me as a payment{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.23,正文,,0,0,0,,作为一直给他提供免费食物的报酬\N{\fs16}for all the free meals she's given him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.43,正文,,0,0,0,,反正兄弟会又不想要我\N{\fs16}Anyway, it's not me the Brotherhood wants.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.90,正文,,0,0,0,,我的兄弟可不是国王\N{\fs16}My brother ain't no king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:54.57,正文,,0,0,0,,我也不是凝冬城的史塔克\N{\fs16}I'm not a Stark of Winterhell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.00,正文,,0,0,0,,临冬城\N{\fs16}Winterfell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.51,正文,,0,0,0,,- 真的？ - 当然\N{\fs16}- You sure? - I'm sure.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.68,正文,,0,0,0,,还有 这个是给你做的\N{\fs16}Well, I made you something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.99,正文,,0,0,0,,这是什么？\N{\fs16}What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.26,正文,,0,0,0,,是个狼啊\N{\fs16}It's a wolf.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.39,0:14:19.33,正文,,0,0,0,,没错 是个狼\N{\fs16}Yes, it is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.96,正文,,0,0,0,,这是它的尾巴？\N{\fs16}That's the tail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.50,正文,,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs16}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.87,正文,,0,0,0,,好了 注意安全\N{\fs16}Well, be safe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:29.74,正文,,0,0,0,,嗯 你也是\N{\fs16}Yeah, you, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.47,正文,,0,0,0,,别受伤\N{\fs16}Don't get stabbed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.41,正文,,0,0,0,,你也……\N{\fs16}You don't...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.28,正文,,0,0,0,,别烧到手指\N{\fs16}burn your fingers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.76,正文,,0,0,0,,再见 热派\N{\fs16}Good-bye, Hot Pie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:51.06,正文,,0,0,0,,再见 阿利\N{\fs16}Good-bye, Arry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:03.97,正文,,0,0,0,,上马吧 小小姐\N{\fs16}Up you go, little lady.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.68,正文,,0,0,0,,喂 热派\N{\fs16}Hey, Hot Pie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:16.99,正文,,0,0,0,,真的很好吃\N{\fs16}It's really good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:25.63,正文,,0,0,0,,某人居然忘记了有仗在打\N{\fs16}A person could almost be forgiven{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.86,正文,,0,0,0,,这可不好原谅啊\N{\fs16}for forgetting we're at war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:34.70,正文,,0,0,0,,对于世界上大部分地方来说 即便处于战争最黑暗的时期\N{\fs16}It often comforts me to think that even in war's darkest days,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.57,正文,,0,0,0,,也根本什么都没有发生\N{\fs16}in most places in the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:40.87,正文,,0,0,0,,这样想常会让我心里安慰许多\N{\fs16}absolutely nothing is happening.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.25,正文,,0,0,0,,我很想念你 叔叔\N{\fs16}I've missed you, Uncle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.25,正文,,0,0,0,,你离开这么久\N{\fs16}Father missed you, too,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.18,正文,,0,0,0,,父亲也很想念你\N{\fs16}from the day you left.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.22,0:15:51.39,正文,,0,0,0,,或许他从来没有说出来过――\N{\fs16}Maybe he never said it in so many words--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.02,正文,,0,0,0,,或许？\N{\fs16}Maybe?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.32,正文,,0,0,0,,你父亲是头顽固的老公牛\N{\fs16}Your father was a stubborn old ox.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:57.13,正文,,0,0,0,,他死的时候我很惊讶\N{\fs16}I was surprised when he died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.93,正文,,0,0,0,,还以为死神对他没有那个耐性\N{\fs16}Didn't think death had the patience.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.87,正文,,0,0,0,,你当时能陪在他身边实在太好了\N{\fs16}I'm glad you were with him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.77,正文,,0,0,0,,我多希望诸神让我当时也能在场\N{\fs16}I wish to the gods I had been.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.37,0:16:12.17,正文,,0,0,0,,你们最终和解了吗？\N{\fs16}Did you make peace in the end?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.21,0:16:15.01,正文,,0,0,0,,吵了三十年\N{\fs16}After 30 years of fighting,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.45,正文,,0,0,0,,大概他已经不记得最初是因为什么了\N{\fs16}I don't think he remembered what started it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.48,0:16:21.22,正文,,0,0,0,,他叫我别再自称黑鱼\N{\fs16}He asked me to stop calling myself Blackfish.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:23.42,正文,,0,0,0,,他说那是个老掉牙的笑话\N{\fs16}He said it was an old joke{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.95,正文,,0,0,0,,而且从一开始就不好笑\N{\fs16}and it was never funny to begin with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:29.99,正文,,0,0,0,,我告诉他 人们早已习惯叫我黑鱼\N{\fs16}I told him people had been calling me Blackfish{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.90,正文,,0,0,0,,这么长时间之后 我的本名都被忘了\N{\fs16}for so long, they don't remember my real name.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.24,正文,,0,0,0,,每次他离开奔流城去君临\N{\fs16}Every time he would leave for the capital{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:42.00,正文,,0,0,0,,或者去参加比武大会\N{\fs16}or fight in a campaign,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.07,0:16:44.17,正文,,0,0,0,,我都会看着他离开\N{\fs16}I'd see him off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:47.31,正文,,0,0,0,,他会说 “等着我回来 小凯特”\N{\fs16}"Wait for me, little Cat," he'd say.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:50.51,正文,,0,0,0,,“等着我\N{\fs16}"Wait for me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:54.02,正文,,0,0,0,,我很快就会回来的”\N{\fs16}and I'll come back to you."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.58,正文,,0,0,0,,每天太阳升起的时候\N{\fs16}And I would sit at this window{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:59.35,正文,,0,0,0,,我就坐在这个窗边等他\N{\fs16}every day when the sun came up, waiting.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:05.53,正文,,0,0,0,,我常常想\N{\fs16}I wonder{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:08.30,正文,,0,0,0,,布兰和瑞肯有多少次\N{\fs16}how many times did Bran or Rickon{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:10.26,正文,,0,0,0,,在眺望临冬城的旷野\N{\fs16}stare across the moors of Winterfell{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.47,正文,,0,0,0,,等着我回去\N{\fs16}waiting for me to return.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.50,0:17:15.97,正文,,0,0,0,,我再也见不到他们了\N{\fs16}I will never see them again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.14,正文,,0,0,0,,别这么想\N{\fs16}You mustn't think it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:23.48,正文,,0,0,0,,我们还不知道确切情况\N{\fs16}We don't know the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:26.18,正文,,0,0,0,,他们可能藏起来了\N{\fs16}They could be in hiding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:31.99,正文,,0,0,0,,罗柏相信他们还活着\N{\fs16}Robb believes they're alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.02,0:17:34.16,正文,,0,0,0,,他坚信这一点\N{\fs16}And he must go on believing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.96,正文,,0,0,0,,要打胜仗罗柏必须坚强\N{\fs16}He's got to remain strong if he's to prevail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:41.06,正文,,0,0,0,,你为了他也要坚强下去\N{\fs16}And you must remain strong for him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:53.84,正文,,0,0,0,,你是罗柏・史塔克的妻子\N{\fs16}You're Robb Stark's wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.34,正文,,0,0,0,,别乱动\N{\fs16}Hold still.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.61,正文,,0,0,0,,他们说的他那些事是真的吗？\N{\fs16}Is it true what they say about him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.65,0:18:03.22,正文,,0,0,0,,我不知道 他们说他什么？\N{\fs16}I don't know. What do they say about him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:05.52,正文,,0,0,0,,说他晚上会变成一头狼\N{\fs16}That he can turn into a wolf at night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.26,正文,,0,0,0,,是真的\N{\fs16}True.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.53,正文,,0,0,0,,还说他会生吃敌人的血肉\N{\fs16}And he eats the flesh of his enemies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:12.53,正文,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs16}True.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.80,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(361.783,206.656)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}威廉・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.50,正文,,0,0,0,,你姓兰尼斯特 是么？\N{\fs16}You're a Lannister, aren't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.73,正文,,0,0,0,,马丁・兰尼斯特\N{\fs16}Martyn Lannister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:22.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(511.116,235.899)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}马丁・兰尼斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.90,正文,,0,0,0,,马丁・兰尼斯特\N{\fs16}Martyn Lannister.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.20,正文,,0,0,0,,你不必害怕\N{\fs16}You've nothing to fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:25.37,正文,,0,0,0,,我丈夫不吃小孩\N{\fs16}My husband doesn't eat children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:29.48,正文,,0,0,0,,除非是满月\N{\fs16}Unless it's a full moon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:32.31,正文,,0,0,0,,今天晚上不是满月吧？\N{\fs16}It's not a full moon tonight, is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:34.11,正文,,0,0,0,,看到没？\N{\fs16}See?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:36.38,正文,,0,0,0,,不必害怕\N{\fs16}Nothing to fear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.20,0:18:56.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(252.478,247.332)}{\pos(470,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}曼斯・雷德{\b0}\N{\fs12}“塞外之王”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:56.91,正文,,0,0,0,,还是这么艺术啊\N{\fs16}Always the artists.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.33,0:19:18.76,正文,,0,0,0,,只有马的尸体\N{\fs16}It's only horses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.90,0:19:20.60,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(126.499,276.848)}{\pos(300,260)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}琼恩・雪诺{\b0}\N{\fs12}叛逃的乌鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.40,正文,,0,0,0,,没有人的\N{\fs16}No men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:24.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(126,233.211)}{\pos(470,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}耶哥蕊特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“火吻而生” 野人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.14,正文,,0,0,0,,你不是说有不少死乌鸦嘛\N{\fs16}You said there was dead crows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:26.50,正文,,0,0,0,,本来有\N{\fs16}There was.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.40,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(517.899,251.5)}{\pos(470,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}欧瑞尔{\b0}\N{\fs12}“鹰眼” 易形者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:30.31,正文,,0,0,0,,一共有多少人\N{\fs16}How many men were here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.54,正文,,0,0,0,,大约300人\N{\fs16}About 300.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:34.98,正文,,0,0,0,,你知道这些人现在怎么样吗？\N{\fs16}And you know what those men are now?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:42.05,正文,,0,0,0,,对异鬼来说我们都一样――他们军队的食物\N{\fs16}We're all the same to them-- meat for their army.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.99,正文,,0,0,0,,你觉得有没有人逃走了？\N{\fs16}Do you think anyone got away?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.02,0:19:47.53,正文,,0,0,0,,不是不可能\N{\fs16}It's not impossible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.93,正文,,0,0,0,,莫尔蒙不容轻视\N{\fs16}You don't go far betting against Mormont.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:52.26,正文,,0,0,0,,但无论是死是活\N{\fs16}But dead or alive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:54.43,正文,,0,0,0,,他北上的这一场豪赌\N{\fs16}he took a big gamble coming north.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:56.53,正文,,0,0,0,,都已失败\N{\fs16}And he lost.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:19:58.90,正文,,0,0,0,,他手下最能打的人全都死了\N{\fs16}His best fighting men are dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:02.14,正文,,0,0,0,,不管他是守夜人军团的司令官\N{\fs16}And whether he's Lord Commander of the Night's Watch{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.17,0:20:04.14,正文,,0,0,0,,还是一具蓝眼睛的尸体\N{\fs16}or a blue-eyed corpse,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.98,正文,,0,0,0,,他都离长城远得很\N{\fs16}he's a long way from home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.38,正文,,0,0,0,,托蒙德\N{\fs16}Tormund.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.42,正文,,0,0,0,,翻过长城\N{\fs16}Climb the Wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:14.52,正文,,0,0,0,,带上欧瑞尔 挑20个好手\N{\fs16}Take Orell and 20 good men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(133.01,270.109)}{\pos(470,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}托蒙德{\b0}\N{\fs12}“巨人克星” 野人掠袭者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.15,正文,,0,0,0,,把他也带上\N{\fs16}And take this one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.02,正文,,0,0,0,,黑城堡的防御他比我们所有人都熟\N{\fs16}He knows Castle Black's defenses better than any of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:21.46,正文,,0,0,0,,如果他有用 那当然好 否则……\N{\fs16}And if he's useful, good. If not...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.49,0:20:23.89,正文,,0,0,0,,把他从城墙上扔下去\N{\fs16}throw him off the Wall.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:26.83,正文,,0,0,0,,看看乌鸦到底会不会飞\N{\fs16}See if crows can fly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:30.17,正文,,0,0,0,,终于要打仗了吗 老朋友？\N{\fs16}We're finally going to war, old friend?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.77,正文,,0,0,0,,在黑城堡附近藏起来\N{\fs16}Hide near Castle Black.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:34.10,正文,,0,0,0,,收到我的信号之后 趁晚上偷袭他们\N{\fs16}When I give the signal, hit them in the night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.84,正文,,0,0,0,,他们可以依着巨大的长城防守\N{\fs16}They've got a big old wall to hide behind,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.87,0:20:38.71,正文,,0,0,0,,但是长城只能防守北面\N{\fs16}but it only guards one side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.91,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我们会再见面的 - 没错\N{\fs16}- We'll meet again. - Aye.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:44.11,正文,,0,0,0,,- 只要你事情办妥了 - 哈\N{\fs16}- If you do your job. - Ah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:46.32,正文,,0,0,0,,我们怎么收到你的信号？\N{\fs16}How will we see your signal?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.35,0:20:49.05,正文,,0,0,0,,每天晚上让你的鹰飞到长城上方\N{\fs16}Send your eagle above the Wall every night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.86,正文,,0,0,0,,时机到了 我会点燃北境所见过的\N{\fs16}When it's time, I'm going to light the biggest fire{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.09,正文,,0,0,0,,最大的一团火焰\N{\fs16}the North has ever seen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(542.122,249.244)}{\pos(480,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}山姆威尔・塔利{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人事务官
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.92,正文,,0,0,0,,白灵？\N{\fs16}Ghost?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:24.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(117.747,171.863)}{\pos(200,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}白灵{\b0}\N{\fs12}琼恩・雪诺的冰原狼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.17,0:21:39.87,正文,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这是什么？冻僵的乌鸦？\N{\fs16}What have we here? Frozen crows?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.91,0:21:41.91,正文,,0,0,0,,我们赶了很远的路\N{\fs16}We've come a long way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.21,0:21:46.68,正文,,0,0,0,,比你来时少了很多人啊\N{\fs16}Smaller flock than you went north with.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:48.82,正文,,0,0,0,,我们可以进去谈\N{\fs16}We can talk inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:49.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(298.302,272.458)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}杰奥・莫尔蒙{\b0}\N{\fs12}“熊老” 守夜人总司令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:51.95,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗？\N{\fs16}Oh, can we?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(298.302,272.458)}{\pos(250,190)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}卡斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}野人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:02.30,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(310.927,277.68)}{\pos(80,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}葛兰{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人游骑兵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:14.54,正文,,0,0,0,,他们需要些水\N{\fs16}They need some water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.58,0:22:16.74,正文,,0,0,0,,把它拴起来 我马上进来\N{\fs16}Tether it and I'll be inside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.50,0:22:29.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(326.164,279.954)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}雷斯特{\b0}\N{\fs12}守夜人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:34.53,正文,,0,0,0,,管好你们的眼睛\N{\fs16}Keep your eyes where they belong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.10,正文,,0,0,0,,她们不是你能看的\N{\fs16}They're not for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.13,0:22:39.60,正文,,0,0,0,,我敢说你喂猪的食物也比给我们的好\N{\fs16}Bet you feed that pig better than you feed us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.63,0:22:43.07,正文,,0,0,0,,没错 猪对我来说有用\N{\fs16}Aye, pig's got value to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.10,0:22:46.97,正文,,0,0,0,,我让你们进来你们就该亲我的脚了\N{\fs16}You should all be kissing my feet for letting you in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.31,0:22:51.14,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我不是个信神的人我早让你们全滚蛋了\N{\fs16}I'd have turned you all away if I wasn't a godly man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:53.51,正文,,0,0,0,,你信神？\N{\fs16}You are a godly man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.98,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 我不害怕外面发生什么\N{\fs16}I am. I got no fear of what's out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.02,0:22:59.02,正文,,0,0,0,,当白色寒神来临时\N{\fs16}When the white cold comes,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.05,0:23:03.19,正文,,0,0,0,,你们的剑和斗篷还有他妈的火堆都帮不了你\N{\fs16}your swords and cloaks and bloody fires won't help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:07.46,正文,,0,0,0,,只有信对了神的人才能活下来\N{\fs16}The only ones left will be those who are right with the gods.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.49,0:23:09.06,正文,,0,0,0,,信奉真神的人\N{\fs16}The real gods.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:17.34,正文,,0,0,0,,去告诉她 要么咬个破布\N{\fs16}Go tell her she can bite down on a rag{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.37,0:23:20.04,正文,,0,0,0,,要么就等着我的拳头\N{\fs16}or she can bite down on my fist.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.11,0:23:26.55,正文,,0,0,0,,女人\N{\fs16}Women.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:28.45,正文,,0,0,0,,那只母猪就在那\N{\fs16}That sow right there gave birth{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:30.78,正文,,0,0,0,,生了八只小猪\N{\fs16}to a litter of eight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:32.95,正文,,0,0,0,,都没哼哼一下\N{\fs16}Barely a grunt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:37.32,正文,,0,0,0,,她也就跟这家伙差不多肥\N{\fs16}And she's almost as fat as this one here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:40.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(121.954,257.294)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}艾迪森・托勒特{\b0}\N{\fs12}“忧郁的艾迪”  守夜人事务官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.36,0:23:39.93,正文,,0,0,0,,你们怎么不吃了他？\N{\fs16}Now why don't you dine on him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:42.60,正文,,0,0,0,,走的时候切下几块来带走\N{\fs16}Carve off what you need as you go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:45.76,正文,,0,0,0,,看看他 根本就是会走路的美食嘛\N{\fs16}Well, look at him. He's a walking feast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:05.25,正文,,0,0,0,,快了快了\N{\fs16}Here we are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.28,0:24:07.65,正文,,0,0,0,,给我磨锋利点 好吗？\N{\fs16}Sharpen these for me, would ya?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.54,0:24:27.24,正文,,0,0,0,,我看到头了 用力\N{\fs16}I see the head. Push.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.04,正文,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fs16}That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.08,0:24:32.41,正文,,0,0,0,,就快生出来了\N{\fs16}You're nearly there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.20,0:24:37.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(548.621,267.041)}{\pos(300,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}吉莉{\b0}\N{\fs12}卡斯特的女儿与妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:38.82,正文,,0,0,0,,再用点力就生出来了\N{\fs16}One more push should do it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.80,0:24:51.13,正文,,0,0,0,,男孩女孩？男孩女孩？\N{\fs16}What is it? What is it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:25.10,正文,,0,0,0,,别做声\N{\fs16}Keep quiet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.20,0:25:30.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(564.987,262.72)}{\pos(250,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}席恩・葛雷乔伊{\b0}\N{\fs12}铁群岛继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.33,0:25:57.17,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你不能骑马 我们就完了\N{\fs16}If you can't ride, we don't stand a chance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.20,0:25:59.24,正文,,0,0,0,,我能骑\N{\fs16}I can ride.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.27,0:26:01.54,正文,,0,0,0,,你确定？\N{\fs16}You're sure?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.09,0:26:17.32,正文,,0,0,0,,往东骑 跟着升起的太阳\N{\fs16}Ride east. Follow the rising sun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.35,0:26:19.76,正文,,0,0,0,,你姐姐在等着你\N{\fs16}Your sister's waiting for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.79,0:26:22.49,正文,,0,0,0,,我会报答你的 我会封你做铁群岛的头领\N{\fs16}I'll make you a Lord of the Iron Islands for this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.53,0:26:23.69,正文,,0,0,0,,我们可不在铁群岛\N{\fs16}We're not in the Iron Islands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:26.26,正文,,0,0,0,,- 快走 - 驾\N{\fs16}- Go. - Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.30,0:26:27.90,正文,,0,0,0,,驾 驾\N{\fs16}Come on. Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.93,0:26:29.87,正文,,0,0,0,,驾 驾\N{\fs16}Come on. Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.77,0:26:35.74,正文,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs16}Come on back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.48,0:26:41.64,正文,,0,0,0,,你不打算告诉我你要去哪？\N{\fs16}You refuse to tell me where you're going?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.71,0:26:44.78,正文,,0,0,0,,我还不知道 圣火会指示我的\N{\fs16}I don't know yet. The fires will show me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.81,0:26:47.55,正文,,0,0,0,,- 你会去多久？ - 我不知道\N{\fs16}- How long will you be gone? - I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.12,0:26:50.25,正文,,0,0,0,,你要抛弃我\N{\fs16}You're abandoning me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.29,0:26:52.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我绝对不会抛弃你\N{\fs16}I will never abandon you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.50,0:26:56.50,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(557.021,286.714)}{\pos(100,300)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}史坦尼斯・拜拉席恩{\b0}\N{\fs12}狭海中的王
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.26,0:26:56.42,正文,,0,0,0,,你是圣焰之子\N{\fs16}You are the Son of Fire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.46,0:26:58.99,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我发誓效忠于你  - 那就留下\N{\fs16}- I am sworn to serve you. - Then serve me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.03,0:27:01.20,正文,,0,0,0,,当我回来的时候 你会明白的\N{\fs16}When I return, you will understand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.63,0:27:05.80,正文,,0,0,0,,敌人认为我已经被彻底击败了\N{\fs16}My enemies think they've destroyed me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.70,0:27:09.87,正文,,0,0,0,,他们在嘲笑我\N{\fs16}They're laughing at me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.91,0:27:13.41,正文,,0,0,0,,像蓝礼那样嘲笑我\N{\fs16}the way Renly laughed at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.44,0:27:16.01,正文,,0,0,0,,我要乔佛里死\N{\fs16}I want Joffrey dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.05,0:27:18.55,正文,,0,0,0,,我要罗柏・史塔克死\N{\fs16}I want Robb Stark dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.40,0:27:22.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(132.09,267.268)}{\pos(250,300)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}梅丽珊卓{\b0}\N{\fs12}光之王的“红袍祭司”
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.09,0:27:24.15,正文,,0,0,0,,再给我生个孩子\N{\fs16}Make me another son.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.19,0:27:25.79,正文,,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fs16}I cannot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.82,0:27:27.02,正文,,0,0,0,,为什么？\N{\fs16}Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.06,0:27:30.09,正文,,0,0,0,,你的力量不足 这会害死你的\N{\fs16}You don't have the strength. It would kill you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.13,0:27:33.00,正文,,0,0,0,,我没有那么容易死 人们想杀我很久了\N{\fs16}I'm not so easily killed. Men have been trying for years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.80,0:27:40.17,正文,,0,0,0,,我想要你\N{\fs16}I want you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.42,0:27:56.76,正文,,0,0,0,,你的火焰燃烧得很微弱 国王陛下\N{\fs16}Your fires burn low, my king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.89,0:28:03.70,正文,,0,0,0,,还有其它的办法 更好的办法\N{\fs16}There is another way. A better way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.73,0:28:06.30,正文,,0,0,0,,你说过你的魔法需要国王之血才能施放\N{\fs16}You told me your magic requires a king's blood.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.33,0:28:07.93,正文,,0,0,0,,- 是的 - 而我是唯一真正的国王\N{\fs16}- Yes. - I'm the one true king.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.97,0:28:09.53,正文,,0,0,0,,您的确是\N{\fs16}You are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.57,0:28:11.80,正文,,0,0,0,,但是还有人的血管里 也流淌着您的血\N{\fs16}But there are others with your blood in their veins.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.47,0:28:17.01,正文,,0,0,0,,您终将称王于铁王座\N{\fs16}You will sit on the Iron Throne,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.04,0:28:19.18,正文,,0,0,0,,但在此之前 必须要做出牺牲\N{\fs16}but first there must be sacrifices.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.21,0:28:22.01,正文,,0,0,0,,光之王需要祭品\N{\fs16}The Lord of Light demands it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.46,0:28:35.96,正文,,0,0,0,,这条惩罚之路是一个警告 陛下\N{\fs16}The Walk of Punishment is a warning, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.99,0:28:39.10,正文,,0,0,0,,- 给谁的警告？ - 那些胆敢犯罪的奴隶\N{\fs16}- To whom? - To any slave who contemplates doing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.13,0:28:41.80,正文,,0,0,0,,他们的下场便是如此\N{\fs16}whatever these slaves did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.20,0:28:44.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(261.398,283.545)}{\pos(280,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}丹妮莉丝・坦格利安{\b0}\N{\fs12}风暴降生 龙之母
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.83,0:28:44.33,正文,,0,0,0,,水\N{\fs16}Give me your water.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.37,0:28:48.07,正文,,0,0,0,,卡丽熙 这人是个死刑犯\N{\fs16}Khaleesi, this man has been sentenced to death.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.71,0:28:56.35,正文,,0,0,0,,来 喝一点\N{\fs16}Here, drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:29:00.92,正文,,0,0,0,,离开这儿吧 陛下\N{\fs16}Leave this place, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.95,0:29:02.52,正文,,0,0,0,,今晚就走 我恳求您\N{\fs16}Leave tonight, I beg you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.10,0:29:04.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(370.444,207.931)}{\pos(273,272)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}巴利斯坦・赛尔弥\N{\fs12}女王铁卫 “无畏的” 
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.10,0:29:04.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(158.699,215.812)}{\pos(150,280)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}乔拉・莫尔蒙{\b0}\N{\fs12}“大熊” 熊老之子
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.59,0:29:04.05,正文,,0,0,0,,那招兵的事儿怎么办？\N{\fs16}And what is she to do for soldiers?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.09,0:29:07.56,正文,,0,0,0,,我们可以在潘托斯和密尔找到雇佣兵\N{\fs16}We can find sellswords in Pentos and Myr.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.63,0:29:11.06,正文,,0,0,0,,你已经开始说“我们”了 巴利斯坦爵士？\N{\fs16}Is it "we" already, Ser Barristan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.10,0:29:14.90,正文,,0,0,0,,如果想重回祖先的王座 您只能武力夺取\N{\fs16}If you want to sit on the throne your ancestors built, you must win it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.93,0:29:17.13,正文,,0,0,0,,这意味着在此之前 您的手上将会沾满鲜血\N{\fs16}That will mean blood on your hands before the thing is done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.17,0:29:20.37,正文,,0,0,0,,沾满敌人的血 而不是无辜者的\N{\fs16}The blood of my enemies, not the blood of innocents.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.77,0:29:25.91,正文,,0,0,0,,你打过几次仗 巴利斯坦爵士？\N{\fs16}How many wars have you fought in, Ser Barristan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.94,0:29:28.18,正文,,0,0,0,,- 三次 - 有哪次\N{\fs16}- Three. - Have you ever seen a war{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.21,0:29:30.58,正文,,0,0,0,,没有牺牲成千上万的无辜者？\N{\fs16}where innocents didn't die by the thousands?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.25,0:29:38.29,正文,,0,0,0,,君临陷落的时候我在场 卡丽熙\N{\fs16}I was in King's Landing after the sack, khaleesi.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.32,0:29:41.46,正文,,0,0,0,,你猜我看到了什么？ 屠杀\N{\fs16}You know what I saw? Butchery.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.49,0:29:43.86,正文,,0,0,0,,婴儿 孩童 老人全都惨遭毒手\N{\fs16}Babies, children, old men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.93,0:29:46.30,正文,,0,0,0,,遭强暴的妇女更是无法尽数\N{\fs16}More women raped than you can count.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.33,0:29:47.93,正文,,0,0,0,,每个人心中都有一头狂暴的野兽\N{\fs16}There's a beast in every man{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.97,0:29:50.93,正文,,0,0,0,,只要武器交到他手中 那头野兽便会蠢蠢欲动\N{\fs16}and it stirs when you put a sword in his hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.00,0:29:53.34,正文,,0,0,0,,但无垢者不是人\N{\fs16}But the Unsullied are not men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.37,0:29:55.00,正文,,0,0,0,,他们不会强暴妇女\N{\fs16}They do not rape.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.04,0:29:58.11,正文,,0,0,0,,除非指挥官明确下令 他们不会劫掠城市\N{\fs16}They do not put cities to the sword unless they're ordered to do so.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.14,0:30:02.81,正文,,0,0,0,,如果您买下他们 他们会只杀您想杀的人\N{\fs16}If you buy them, the only men they'll kill are those you want dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.85,0:30:04.31,正文,,0,0,0,,你不这样认为吗 巴利斯坦爵士？\N{\fs16}Do you disagree, Ser Barristan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.35,0:30:07.42,正文,,0,0,0,,当您的兄长雷加 率领军队在三叉戟河作战时\N{\fs16}When your brother Rhaegar led his army into battle at the Trident,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.45,0:30:10.09,正文,,0,0,0,,人们为他而死 是因为他们信任他\N{\fs16}men died for him because they believed in him,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.12,0:30:11.82,正文,,0,0,0,,因为他们爱他\N{\fs16}because they loved him,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.86,0:30:14.32,正文,,0,0,0,,而非因为他拍卖会上出价最高\N{\fs16}not because they'd been bought at a slaver's auction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.26,0:30:18.90,正文,,0,0,0,,那一天 我曾与最后的真龙并肩作战 陛下\N{\fs16}I fought beside the last dragon on that day, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.63,0:30:22.73,正文,,0,0,0,,我为他而负伤\N{\fs16}I bled beside him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.77,0:30:26.30,正文,,0,0,0,,雷加战斗得英勇 雷加战斗得高贵\N{\fs16}Rhaegar fought valiantly, Rhaegar fought nobly,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.34,0:30:28.17,正文,,0,0,0,,雷加死得不明不白\N{\fs16}and Rhaegar died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.14,0:30:31.74,正文,,0,0,0,,你很了解雷加吗 巴利斯坦爵士？\N{\fs16}Did you know him well, Ser Barristan?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.78,0:30:36.31,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 陛下 他是我见过的最好的人\N{\fs16}I did, Your Grace. Finest man I ever met.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.38,0:30:38.55,正文,,0,0,0,,我希望我也能认识他\N{\fs16}I wish I had known him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.58,0:30:40.62,正文,,0,0,0,,但他并非最后的真龙\N{\fs16}But he was not the last dragon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.55,0:30:52.61,正文,,0,0,0,,所有的？\N{\fs16}All?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.64,0:30:55.23,正文,,0,0,0,,小人听错了吗 陛下？\N{\fs16}Did this one's ears mishear, Your Grace?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.77,0:30:58.00,正文,,0,0,0,,你没有 我要买下所有的无垢者\N{\fs16}They did not. I want to buy them all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.10,0:31:00.40,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她想把他们全买下来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:04.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(573.664,262.029)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}格雷赞\N{\b0}{\fs12}阿斯塔波的奴隶主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:04.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(444.775,262.915)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}克拉兹尼・莫・纳克罗兹{\b0}\N{\fs12}阿斯塔波的奴隶主
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.20,0:31:04.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(333.441,261.702)}{\pos(50,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}弥桑黛{\b0}\N{\fs12}奴隶翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:02.80,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她买不起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.20,0:31:06.80,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}这荡妇以为给我们瞅瞅她的奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.80,0:31:10.70,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(313,298)}就能予取予夺了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.82,0:31:16.29,正文,,0,0,0,,阿斯塔波一共有8000名无垢者\N{\fs16}There are 8,000 Unsullied in Astapor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.32,0:31:18.06,正文,,0,0,0,,这就是您指的“所有的”？\N{\fs16}Is this what you mean by all?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.09,0:31:19.99,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 8000名\N{\fs16}Yes. 8,000.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.06,0:31:22.33,正文,,0,0,0,,仍在训练中的也包括在内\N{\fs16}And the ones still in training as well.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.20,0:31:27.10,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}要是他们打了败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.60,0:31:29.90,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}阿斯塔波会蒙羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.74,0:31:35.11,正文,,0,0,0,,格雷赞主人说他们不能出售未完成训练的男孩\N{\fs16}Master Greizhen says they cannot sell half-trained boys.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.14,0:31:37.44,正文,,0,0,0,,如果他们在战场上失败\N{\fs16}If they fail on the battlefield,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.48,0:31:39.71,正文,,0,0,0,,那会让整个阿斯塔波的名声受损\N{\fs16}they will bring shame upon all of Astapor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.75,0:31:41.61,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你们不全数卖给我 我就一个也不买\N{\fs16}I will have them all or take none.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.65,0:31:42.84,正文,,0,0,0,,如果他们在战斗中死亡\N{\fs16}Many will fall in battle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.86,0:31:44.92,正文,,0,0,0,,我需要那些男孩作为替补继续战斗\N{\fs16}I'll need the boys to pick up the swords they drop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.60,0:31:50.00,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}这荡妇钱不够全买下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.89,0:31:52.78,正文,,0,0,0,,克拉兹尼主人说您付不起这么多钱\N{\fs16}Master Kraznys says you cannot afford this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.35,0:31:56.95,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她的船够买100个无垢者 不能再多了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.95,0:31:57.60,正文,,0,0,0,,您的船可以换来100名无垢者\N{\fs16}Your ship will buy you 100 Unsullied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.60,0:32:01.00,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}这还是因为我喜欢她臀部的线条
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:04.77,正文,,0,0,0,,这还是出于克拉兹尼主人的慷慨大方\N{\fs16}Because Master Kraznys is generous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.90,0:32:07.45,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}剩下的财物还够买10个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.45,0:32:09.20,正文,,0,0,0,,您剩下的金子只能买下10名\N{\fs16}The gold you have left is worth 10.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.20,0:32:13.10,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她别像白痴一样哭哭啼啼我就给她算成20个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.40,0:32:12.70,正文,,0,0,0,,但善良的克拉兹尼主人会卖给您20名\N{\fs16}But good Master Kraznys will give you 20.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:17.35,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她那群多斯拉克人闻起来像屎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.00,0:32:17.00,正文,,0,0,0,,您带领的多斯拉克人――\N{\fs16}The Dothraki you have with you--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.70,0:32:21.50,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}拿来喂猪倒可能不错
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.92,0:32:25.73,正文,,0,0,0,,您带领的多斯拉克人 还不如他们吃掉的东西有价值\N{\fs16}The Dothraki you have are not worth what they cost to feed,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.60,0:32:28.15,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}也就再值3个
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.76,0:32:27.90,正文,,0,0,0,,但是克拉兹尼主人会用3名无垢者\N{\fs16}but Master Kraznys will give you three Unsullied{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.33,0:32:29.90,正文,,0,0,0,,来交换这些人\N{\fs16}for all of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.10,0:32:33.00,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}所以问问这个讨饭的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:36.67,正文,,0,0,0,,剩下7877名无垢者的价格\N{\fs16}for the remaining 7,877 Unsullied.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.80,0:32:37.00,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(313,298)}剩下的7877个她打算怎么买
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.71,0:32:47.61,正文,,0,0,0,,我还有龙 我可以给你们一条\N{\fs16}I have dragons. I'll give you one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.52,0:32:54.39,正文,,0,0,0,,您应当用龙 而非奴隶 来夺回王座 陛下\N{\fs16}You will win the throne with dragons, not slaves, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.42,0:32:57.12,正文,,0,0,0,,卡丽熙 求求您\N{\fs16}Khaleesi, please.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.07,0:33:07.77,正文,,0,0,0,,我要三条龙\N{\fs16}Three dragons.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.80,0:33:09.07,正文,,0,0,0,,- 一条 - 两条\N{\fs16}- One. - Two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.14,0:33:10.44,正文,,0,0,0,,一条\N{\fs16}One.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.95,0:33:23.18,正文,,0,0,0,,他们想要最大的那一条\N{\fs16}They want the biggest one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.22,0:33:25.65,正文,,0,0,0,,- 成交 - 成交\N{\fs16}- Done. - Done.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.36,0:33:33.03,正文,,0,0,0,,我还要把你也带走 就现在\N{\fs16}I'll take you as well, now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.40,0:33:33.00,正文,,0,0,0,,克拉兹尼主人想要知道您想如何支付\N{\fs16}Master Kraznys asks how you propose to pay{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.06,0:33:36.00,正文,,0,0,0,,你将会是克拉兹尼主人送给我的礼物\N{\fs16}You'll be Master Kraznys' gift to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.03,0:33:38.16,正文,,0,0,0,,一个讨价还价的战利品\N{\fs16}A token of a bargain well struck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.70,0:33:42.90,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(315.667,275.847)}她要求把我作为礼物送给她
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.90,0:33:45.20,正文,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(313,298)}她现在就要
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.88,0:33:52.01,正文,,0,0,0,,卡丽熙 一条龙的价值比任何军队都高\N{\fs16}Khaleesi, a dragon is worth more than any army.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.05,0:33:54.31,正文,,0,0,0,,伊耿・坦格利安早就证明过这一点\N{\fs16}Aegon Targaryen proved that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.88,0:33:57.92,正文,,0,0,0,,你们都是来给我出谋划策的\N{\fs16}You're both here to advise me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.95,0:33:59.94,正文,,0,0,0,,我重视你们的建议 但如果你们再次\N{\fs16}I value your advice, but if you ever question me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.96,0:34:01.49,正文,,0,0,0,,在他人面前质疑我\N{\fs16}in front of strangers again,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.49,0:34:04.02,正文,,0,0,0,,你们就另谋高就吧\N{\fs16}you'll be advising someone else.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.06,0:34:06.36,正文,,0,0,0,,明白了吗？\N{\fs16}Is that understood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.10,0:34:10.83,正文,,0,0,0,,你有名字吗？\N{\fs16}Do you have a name?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.86,0:34:13.50,正文,,0,0,0,,小人名叫弥桑黛 陛下\N{\fs16}This one's name is Missandei, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.53,0:34:15.73,正文,,0,0,0,,你有家人吗？如果可能回家的话\N{\fs16}Do you have a family? A mother and a father{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.77,0:34:17.77,正文,,0,0,0,,有在家等你的父母吗？\N{\fs16}you'd return to if you had the choice?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:21.11,正文,,0,0,0,,没有 陛下 我的家人都不在了\N{\fs16}No, Your Grace. No family living.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.14,0:34:24.28,正文,,0,0,0,,那从现在起你属于我了 你的职责就是告诉我真相\N{\fs16}You belong to me now. It is your duty to tell me the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.31,0:34:26.88,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 陛下 欺骗是重罪\N{\fs16}Yes, Your Grace. Lying is a great offense.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.91,0:34:30.28,正文,,0,0,0,,很多惩罚之路上的罪人 犯得罪甚至比这要轻得多\N{\fs16}Many of those on the Walk of Punishment were taken there for less.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.32,0:34:33.04,正文,,0,0,0,,在惩罚之路上 我给了一名濒死的奴隶一些水喝\N{\fs16}I offered water to one of the slaves dying on the Walk of Punishment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.05,0:34:36.32,正文,,0,0,0,,你知道他对我说了什么吗？ “让我死吧”\N{\fs16}Do you know what he said to me? "Let me die."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.36,0:34:39.22,正文,,0,0,0,,死了之后就没有奴隶主虐待他们了 陛下\N{\fs16}There are no masters in the grave, Your Grace.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.39,0:34:41.89,正文,,0,0,0,,关于无垢者的事情\N{\fs16}Is it true what Master Kraznys told me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.93,0:34:45.06,正文,,0,0,0,,克拉兹尼说的是真的吗？他们真的绝对服从？\N{\fs16}about the Unsullied? About their obedience?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.13,0:34:47.63,正文,,0,0,0,,他们不会心生疑虑\N{\fs16}All questions have been taken from them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.67,0:34:49.53,正文,,0,0,0,,只会服从 别无二意\N{\fs16}They obey, that is all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.57,0:34:52.34,正文,,0,0,0,,一旦被您买下 他们就属于您\N{\fs16}Once they are yours, they are yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.37,0:34:54.44,正文,,0,0,0,,就算您命令他们自杀 他们也会照做\N{\fs16}They will fall on their swords if you command it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.47,0:34:57.94,正文,,0,0,0,,那你呢？你知道么 我将把你带入战场\N{\fs16}And what about you? You know that I'm taking you to war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.98,0:35:02.11,正文,,0,0,0,,你可能会饿肚子 你可能会生病\N{\fs16}You may go hungry. You may fall sick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.15,0:35:04.28,正文,,0,0,0,,你可能会被杀\N{\fs16}You may be killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.32,0:35:06.02,正文,,0,0,0,,Valar morghulis.\N{\fs16}Valar morghulis.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.05,0:35:09.62,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 男人皆有一死\N{\fs16}Yes, all men must die.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.66,0:35:12.79,正文,,0,0,0,,但我们是女人\N{\fs16}But we are not men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.83,0:35:26.27,正文,,0,0,0,,用这地儿来保管王室账单 还真是出人意料啊\N{\fs16}A surprising place to keep the royal ledgers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.30,0:35:28.41,正文,,0,0,0,,你这么惊讶才让真是出人意料\N{\fs16}I'm surprised you're surprised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.30,0:35:31.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(338.889,288.165)}{\pos(250,240)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}波德瑞克・派恩{\b0}\N{\fs12}提利昂的侍从
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.04,0:35:33.44,正文,,0,0,0,,这是全城最安全的地方\N{\fs16}This is the safest place in the city.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.48,0:35:35.38,正文,,0,0,0,,对于野种来说并非如此吧\N{\fs16}Not for bastards.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.41,0:35:37.72,正文,,0,0,0,,所有的都在这里了 大人\N{\fs16}That's all of them, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.75,0:35:40.85,正文,,0,0,0,,谢谢 亲爱的 波德\N{\fs16}Thank you, my dear. Pod.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.82,0:35:44.06,正文,,0,0,0,,波德 把它们拿出去\N{\fs16}Pod. Take them outside.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.09,0:35:46.79,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我随后就会到 - 好的 大人\N{\fs16}- I'll be there in a moment. - Yes, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.50,0:35:54.80,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(130.742,247.841)}{\pos(50,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}萝丝{\b0}\N{\fs12}妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.57,0:36:00.84,正文,,0,0,0,,我听说你欠那个男孩很大一笔债\N{\fs16}I hear you owe that boy a significant debt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.87,0:36:02.67,正文,,0,0,0,,我的一条命而已\N{\fs16}Only my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.71,0:36:04.64,正文,,0,0,0,,恐怕没有你说的那么大\N{\fs16}Not all that significant, I'm afraid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.71,0:36:06.71,正文,,0,0,0,,你应当封他为骑士\N{\fs16}You should have him knighted.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.75,0:36:09.91,正文,,0,0,0,,如果财政大臣有这权力 我一定会的\N{\fs16}If only the Master of Coin had such power.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.95,0:36:13.02,正文,,0,0,0,,如果\N{\fs16}If only.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.95,0:36:17.16,正文,,0,0,0,,我也欠你很大一笔债\N{\fs16}I owe you a significant debt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.19,0:36:19.56,正文,,0,0,0,,我们红头发的朋友\N{\fs16}Our redheaded friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.59,0:36:22.36,正文,,0,0,0,,是你把她从太后手里保释出来的\N{\fs16}You secured her release when the queen detained her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.39,0:36:24.36,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 这个啊\N{\fs16}Oh, that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.43,0:36:27.56,正文,,0,0,0,,当然了 那只是个小误会\N{\fs16}Of course. A simple misunderstanding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.60,0:36:29.37,正文,,0,0,0,,显然 太后陛下认为\N{\fs16}Apparently, Her Grace believed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.40,0:36:33.44,正文,,0,0,0,,你们二人的关系非同一般\N{\fs16}that you two had some sort of special relationship.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.51,0:36:36.41,正文,,0,0,0,,我们没有 我干过她一次\N{\fs16}We don't. I did fuck her once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.44,0:36:38.48,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我知道 - 但我们没有别的关系\N{\fs16}- I know. - But we don't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.51,0:36:40.14,正文,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs16}I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.18,0:36:41.88,正文,,0,0,0,,但为什么太后会这样想？\N{\fs16}But how would the queen get that idea?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.91,0:36:44.68,正文,,0,0,0,,你怎么不问她呢？\N{\fs16}Why don't you ask her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.99,0:36:50.15,正文,,0,0,0,,对于我的新职务 你有什么建议吗？\N{\fs16}Any advice for me on my new position?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.19,0:36:53.12,正文,,0,0,0,,保持低调\N{\fs16}Keep a low profile.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.16,0:36:56.43,正文,,0,0,0,,如果每次我听到这个笑话\N{\fs16}If I had a gold dragon{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.46,0:36:59.53,正文,,0,0,0,,都可以得到一枚金龙 我现在就比你更有钱了\N{\fs16}for every time I heard that joke, I'd be richer than you are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.56,0:37:01.43,正文,,0,0,0,,你本来就比我更有钱\N{\fs16}Well, you are richer than I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.47,0:37:03.50,正文,,0,0,0,,说得好\N{\fs16}Good point.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.54,0:37:06.87,正文,,0,0,0,,它们只是数字 纸上的数字\N{\fs16}They're only numbers. Numbers on paper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.91,0:37:10.38,正文,,0,0,0,,一旦你理解了这一点 你可以很轻松地控制它们\N{\fs16}Once you understand that, it's easy to make them behave.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.41,0:37:11.94,正文,,0,0,0,,甚至微不足道\N{\fs16}Trivial even.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.98,0:37:13.75,正文,,0,0,0,,你想要接受真正的挑战吗？\N{\fs16}You want a real challenge?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.78,0:37:15.18,正文,,0,0,0,,来尝试一下我的妓女吧\N{\fs16}Try whores.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.22,0:37:17.78,正文,,0,0,0,,我可没少尝试过\N{\fs16}I've tried quite a few.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.82,0:37:20.29,正文,,0,0,0,,我还有好多事情要做\N{\fs16}Well, lots of work to do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.35,0:37:23.06,正文,,0,0,0,,祝你在鹰巢城过得愉快\N{\fs16}Enjoy the Eyrie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.09,0:37:25.09,正文,,0,0,0,,来嘛 我晚点儿再来\N{\fs16}Come on, I'm here later.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.13,0:37:26.96,正文,,0,0,0,,来嘛\N{\fs16}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.53,0:37:32.03,正文,,0,0,0,,我们今晚再见\N{\fs16}Tonight, then.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.57,0:37:36.07,正文,,0,0,0,,似乎是些很无聊的读物\N{\fs16}Looks like dull reading.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.10,0:37:38.37,正文,,0,0,0,,在你看来所有的读物都很无聊吧\N{\fs16}You think all reading is dull reading.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.41,0:37:41.27,正文,,0,0,0,,不只是我 很多色的人都这么想\N{\fs16}It's an opinion I share with some of the finest men I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.20,0:37:43.90,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(201.778,202.95)}{\pos(280,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}波隆{\b0}\N{\fs12}骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.31,0:37:43.91,正文,,0,0,0,,七国历史上那些不为人知的故事 都藏在这些书页里\N{\fs16}The secret history of the Seven Kingdoms is written in these pages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.91,0:37:46.55,正文,,0,0,0,,除非山羊胡大人编造了一串数字\N{\fs16}Unless Lord Twatbeard made up a bunch of numbers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.58,0:37:48.15,正文,,0,0,0,,来掩盖他的真实目的\N{\fs16}to hide what he's really up to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.18,0:37:50.22,正文,,0,0,0,,除非这全是他胡编乱造的 是的\N{\fs16}Unless he made it all up, yes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.25,0:37:52.65,正文,,0,0,0,,- 波德瑞克 跟紧我们 - 是的 大人\N{\fs16}- Podrick, do keep up. - Yes, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.69,0:37:54.96,正文,,0,0,0,,- 波德瑞克 - 是的 大人？\N{\fs16}- Podrick. - Yes, my lord?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.99,0:37:58.36,正文,,0,0,0,,在与我的朋友波隆爵士 商量了许久之后\N{\fs16}After a long consultation with my colleague Ser Bronn,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.39,0:38:00.29,正文,,0,0,0,,我终于想到了一个合适的方法\N{\fs16}I finally found a suitable reward{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.33,0:38:02.63,正文,,0,0,0,,来奖赏你这段时间\N{\fs16}for the services you've provided over and above{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.67,0:38:04.23,正文,,0,0,0,,为我提供的优质服务\N{\fs16}what might be considered reasonable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.27,0:38:06.67,正文,,0,0,0,,告诉我 波德\N{\fs16}Tell me, Pod,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.70,0:38:09.47,正文,,0,0,0,,你曾经和女人睡过吗？\N{\fs16}have you ever been with a woman?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.51,0:38:12.04,正文,,0,0,0,,- 没有 大人 - 太好了\N{\fs16}- No, my lord. - Wonderful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.51,0:38:17.48,正文,,0,0,0,,吉娜最擅长对付处男了\N{\fs16}Genna specializes in first-timers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.10,0:38:20.80,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(160.964,180.494)}{\pos(50,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}吉娜{\b0}\N{\fs12}妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.51,0:38:20.25,正文,,0,0,0,,当然对付非处男也不错\N{\fs16}She's not bad with second-timers, either.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.28,0:38:22.25,正文,,0,0,0,,呃 大人……\N{\fs16}Uh, my lord...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.29,0:38:24.72,正文,,0,0,0,,得亏你一枪刺进那人脸窝 救了我的命\N{\fs16}A fair enough repayment for putting your spear{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.75,0:38:26.96,正文,,0,0,0,,这就是给你的奖励 还成吧？\N{\fs16}through my would-be killer's face, wouldn't you say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.06,0:38:31.86,正文,,0,0,0,,接下来呢\N{\fs16}Now, as it happens,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.90,0:38:34.40,正文,,0,0,0,,玛丽……\N{\fs16}Marei...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.43,0:38:37.70,正文,,0,0,0,,她的身体滑如矛柄\N{\fs16}is quite the spear handler herself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.74,0:38:41.27,正文,,0,0,0,,这是为了感谢你在战火纷飞的时候\N{\fs16}She's here to thank you for staying by my side{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.40,0:38:43.10,片头介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(358.297,212.395)}{\pos(50,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}玛丽{\b0}\N{\fs12}妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.31,0:38:44.04,正文,,0,0,0,,一直守在我的身边\N{\fs16}as the battle raged all around me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.08,0:38:45.91,正文,,0,0,0,,他很帅气\N{\fs16}He's handsome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.94,0:38:49.25,正文,,0,0,0,,你可没告诉过我他有这么帅气\N{\fs16}You didn't tell me he was handsome.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.55,0:38:54.19,正文,,0,0,0,,在这个圈子里\N{\fs16}Kayla is famous from here to Volantis{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.20,0:38:56.10,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(250.741,200.875)}{\pos(50,200)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}凯拉{\b0}\N{\fs12}妓女
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.22,0:38:56.46,正文,,0,0,0,,凯拉的名气甚至远扬至瓦兰提斯\N{\fs16}in certain circles.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.49,0:38:59.09,正文,,0,0,0,,她是世上仅有的四位\N{\fs16}One of four women in the world{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.13,0:39:02.86,正文,,0,0,0,,可以完成弥林结的女人之一\N{\fs16}who can perform a proper Meereenese Knot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.13,0:39:02.86,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\an8}弥林结：本指困扰作者多年的卷五创作难关，此处为彩蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.90,0:39:05.97,正文,,0,0,0,,大人 我还是个……\N{\fs16}My lord, I don't even...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.00,0:39:07.73,正文,,0,0,0,,你总是称呼我为“大人”\N{\fs16}She's here to thank you{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.77,0:39:10.50,正文,,0,0,0,,叫她来是为了感谢\N{\fs16}for being a thoroughly respectful fellow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.54,0:39:13.34,正文,,0,0,0,,你这样出色的侍从的\N{\fs16}who's never once failed to address me as "my lord."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.68,0:39:18.55,正文,,0,0,0,,在我进晚餐之前回来\N{\fs16}Be back in time for my supper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.88,0:39:25.75,正文,,0,0,0,,悠着点 伙计\N{\fs16}Pace yourself, lad.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.79,0:39:28.22,正文,,0,0,0,,这些年来我一直听说\N{\fs16}For years I've heard that Littlefinger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.26,0:39:30.62,正文,,0,0,0,,小指头会变戏法\N{\fs16}is a magician.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.66,0:39:33.63,正文,,0,0,0,,无论何时国王需要钱 他只消双手一搓\N{\fs16}Whenever the crown needs money, he rubs his hands together{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.66,0:39:36.30,正文,,0,0,0,,吹口气 金山银海就出现了\N{\fs16}and, poof, mountains of gold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.33,0:39:38.73,正文,,0,0,0,,让我猜猜 他不会变戏法\N{\fs16}Let me guess. He's not a magician.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.77,0:39:40.70,正文,,0,0,0,,不会\N{\fs16}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.20,0:39:45.14,正文,,0,0,0,,- 他的钱是偷来的？ - 更糟 是借来的\N{\fs16}- He's stealing it? - Worse, he's borrowing it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.11,0:39:47.77,正文,,0,0,0,,那有什么问题？\N{\fs16}What's wrong with that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.81,0:39:51.48,正文,,0,0,0,,我们偿还不起 这就是问题所在\N{\fs16}We can't afford to pay it back, that's what's wrong with it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.51,0:39:53.85,正文,,0,0,0,,铁王座欠了我父亲几百万金龙\N{\fs16}The crown owes millions to my father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.88,0:39:56.22,正文,,0,0,0,,看在他的孙子坐着铁王座的份上\N{\fs16}Seeing as it's his grandson's ass on the throne,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.25,0:39:58.22,正文,,0,0,0,,我猜他会免除这些债务\N{\fs16}I imagine he'll forgive that debt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.25,0:40:00.55,正文,,0,0,0,,免除债务 我的父亲大人？\N{\fs16}Forgive a debt, my father?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.59,0:40:03.02,正文,,0,0,0,,亏你还能活在这个世上 你还真是出奇的天真\N{\fs16}For a man of the world, you're strangely naive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.06,0:40:04.99,正文,,0,0,0,,我以前从来没借过钱\N{\fs16}I've never borrowed money before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.03,0:40:07.39,正文,,0,0,0,,我又不懂这方面的道道\N{\fs16}I'm not clear on the rules.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.43,0:40:08.86,正文,,0,0,0,,那么……\N{\fs16}Well...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.90,0:40:11.10,正文,,0,0,0,,咳咳！\N{\fs16}Ahem!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.13,0:40:15.43,正文,,0,0,0,,基本的原则是\N{\fs16}The basic principle is{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.47,0:40:16.97,正文,,0,0,0,,我借给你钱\N{\fs16}I lend you money,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.00,0:40:19.54,正文,,0,0,0,,在商定的时间过去之后\N{\fs16}and after an agreed upon period of time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.57,0:40:22.18,正文,,0,0,0,,你要连本带利的返还给我\N{\fs16}you return it with interest.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.21,0:40:23.68,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我不还呢？\N{\fs16}And what if I don't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.71,0:40:25.78,正文,,0,0,0,,呃 你必须还\N{\fs16}Well, you have to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.81,0:40:27.15,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我就是不还呢？\N{\fs16}But what if I don't?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.18,0:40:29.51,正文,,0,0,0,,这就是为啥我不会借钱给你\N{\fs16}This is why I don't lend you money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.55,0:40:33.05,正文,,0,0,0,,总之 我担心的不是我父亲\N{\fs16}Anyway, it's not my father I'm worried about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.09,0:40:35.05,正文,,0,0,0,,我担心的是布拉佛斯的铁金库\N{\fs16}It's the Iron Bank of Braavos.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.09,0:40:36.79,正文,,0,0,0,,我欠了他们几千万金龙\N{\fs16}We owe them tens of millions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.82,0:40:41.33,正文,,0,0,0,,如果我们还不上这份债务 铁金库就会赞助我们的敌人\N{\fs16}If we fail to repay these loans, the bank will fund our enemies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.36,0:40:44.50,正文,,0,0,0,,无论通过何种手段 他们总会拿回属于他们的钱\N{\fs16}One way or another, they always get their gold back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.17,0:40:49.07,正文,,0,0,0,,啊 我们的征服英雄回来了\N{\fs16}Ah, the return of the conquering hero.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.10,0:40:51.57,正文,,0,0,0,,他是不是刚旅游回来？\N{\fs16}Does he have a little jaunt in his step?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.60,0:40:53.24,正文,,0,0,0,,这小伙都快跳起舞来了\N{\fs16}The lad's practically skipping.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.27,0:40:54.94,正文,,0,0,0,,你花了挺长时间\N{\fs16}You were gone a long time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.97,0:40:56.78,正文,,0,0,0,,我相信你的钱没白花\N{\fs16}I trust you got your money's worth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.81,0:40:58.44,正文,,0,0,0,,或者我应该说我的钱没白花？\N{\fs16}Or should I say my money's worth?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.88,0:41:03.21,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 这是个礼物 波德瑞克\N{\fs16}Oh, it was a gift, Podrick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.25,0:41:04.98,正文,,0,0,0,,这比我一整年给你的都多\N{\fs16}This is more than I give you in a year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.02,0:41:07.99,正文,,0,0,0,,他是个侍从 你不用付他钱\N{\fs16}He's a squire. You don't pay him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.02,0:41:10.52,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 那这比我一整年给你的要多得多\N{\fs16}Oh, then it's much more than I give you in a year.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.56,0:41:12.46,正文,,0,0,0,,她们没要钱 大人\N{\fs16}They wouldn't take it, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.79,0:41:15.96,正文,,0,0,0,,或许她们想要和新上任的财政大臣\N{\fs16}Maybe they're trying to curry some favor{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.99,0:41:17.36,正文,,0,0,0,,套套近乎\N{\fs16}with the new Master of Coin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.40,0:41:19.50,正文,,0,0,0,,你听说过有妓女拒绝金子的吗？\N{\fs16}Have you ever known a whore to turn down gold?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:22.07,正文,,0,0,0,,只要我给她们 她们就非常开心\N{\fs16}They were happy enough to take it when I gave it to them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.10,0:41:23.80,正文,,0,0,0,,你跟她们说什么了？\N{\fs16}What did you tell them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.83,0:41:25.40,正文,,0,0,0,,我什么也没说\N{\fs16}I didn't tell them anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.44,0:41:28.51,正文,,0,0,0,,- 你对她们做什么了？ - 挺多花样的\N{\fs16}- What did you do to them? - Lots of things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:30.47,正文,,0,0,0,,那她们看上去挺喜欢这些花样的？\N{\fs16}And they seemed to like these things?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.51,0:41:32.04,正文,,0,0,0,,是的 大人\N{\fs16}Yes, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.08,0:41:33.78,正文,,0,0,0,,她们当然会看上去挺喜欢的\N{\fs16}Of course they seemed to like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.81,0:41:35.31,正文,,0,0,0,,付钱就是为了让她们假装喜欢的\N{\fs16}They're paid to seem to like it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.35,0:41:37.58,正文,,0,0,0,,但是她们这次没拿钱\N{\fs16}Only they weren't paid.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.62,0:41:40.55,正文,,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢？姑娘们很喜欢他\N{\fs16}What are you saying? These ladies enjoyed him so much,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.59,0:41:43.19,正文,,0,0,0,,所以她们这次免费为他服务\N{\fs16}they gave him the time for free?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.22,0:41:44.59,正文,,0,0,0,,这就是你想说的吗？\N{\fs16}Is that what you're telling us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.16,0:41:50.43,正文,,0,0,0,,坐下 波德瑞克\N{\fs16}Sit down, Podrick.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.37,0:41:59.47,正文,,0,0,0,,我们需要谈谈细节\N{\fs16}We're going to need details.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.50,0:42:01.91,正文,,0,0,0,,详尽的细节\N{\fs16}Copious details.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.38,0:42:45.18,正文,,0,0,0,,快！快！\N{\fs16}Come on! Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.88,0:42:48.69,正文,,0,0,0,,快啊！\N{\fs16}Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.72,0:42:50.75,正文,,0,0,0,,驾！\N{\fs16}Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.32,0:43:28.76,正文,,0,0,0,,吓！吓！\N{\fs16}Ha! Ha!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.81,0:44:19.25,正文,,0,0,0,,逃亡者什么下场 你知道吧？\N{\fs16}You know how we deal with runaways here, do you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.72,0:44:28.16,正文,,0,0,0,,脱了他的裤子\N{\fs16}Take off his pants.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.19,0:44:30.59,正文,,0,0,0,,不要！不要！\N{\fs16}No! No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.63,0:44:32.26,正文,,0,0,0,,不 不 不！\N{\fs16}No, no, no!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.30,0:44:34.40,正文,,0,0,0,,我要把你操进地里\N{\fs16}I'm gonna fuck you into the dirt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.43,0:44:36.93,正文,,0,0,0,,不 求你了！不 不 不！\N{\fs16}No, please! No, no, no!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.97,0:44:38.53,正文,,0,0,0,,不 不要！\N{\fs16}No, don't!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.10,0:44:42.84,正文,,0,0,0,,不 求你了！\N{\fs16}No, please!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.87,0:44:45.47,正文,,0,0,0,,不！不！\N{\fs16}No! No!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.60,0:45:16.97,正文,,0,0,0,,你这小杂种\N{\fs16}You little bastard.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.82,0:45:28.85,正文,,0,0,0,,来 大人\N{\fs16}Come, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.25,0:45:34.86,正文,,0,0,0,,你离家太远了 况且凛冬将至\N{\fs16}You're a long way from home and winter is coming.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.58,0:46:02.98,正文,,0,0,0,,我要先干那个大个儿婊子\N{\fs16}I'll take the big bitch first.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.02,0:46:06.39,正文,,0,0,0,,当她又湿又爽的时候 你们就能了结了她\N{\fs16}When she's good and wet, you lot can finish her off.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.42,0:46:08.89,正文,,0,0,0,,大人 我是塔斯的布蕾妮\N{\fs16}My lord, I am Brienne of Tarth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.92,0:46:11.26,正文,,0,0,0,,凯特琳・史塔克夫人命我\N{\fs16}Lady Catelyn Stark commanded me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.29,0:46:13.96,正文,,0,0,0,,将詹姆爵士送到君临城\N{\fs16}to deliver Ser Jaime to King's Landing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.99,0:46:15.93,正文,,0,0,0,,凯特琳・史塔克是个大逆不道的贱人\N{\fs16}Catelyn Stark's a treasonous cunt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.96,0:46:17.93,正文,,0,0,0,,上头就吩咐过活捉弑君者\N{\fs16}Orders were to take the Kingslayer alive.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.96,0:46:20.13,正文,,0,0,0,,没他妈提过你\N{\fs16}Nobody said shit about you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.14,0:46:27.24,正文,,0,0,0,,这可是你自找的\N{\fs16}You're only making it worse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.38,0:46:34.01,正文,,0,0,0,,把她带到暗处去\N{\fs16}Take her over there where it's dark.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.05,0:46:35.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我可不想被人看着\N{\fs16}I'd like a little privacy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.55,0:46:39.49,正文,,0,0,0,,过来！\N{\fs16}Come on!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.30,0:46:52.33,正文,,0,0,0,,你知道她是谁 对吧？\N{\fs16}You know who she is, don't you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.90,0:46:58.27,正文,,0,0,0,,大个蠢婊子，谁管她哪来的\N{\fs16}A big dumb bitch from who cares where.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.84,0:47:02.41,正文,,0,0,0,,大到根本算不上是个女人\N{\fs16}Never been with a woman that big.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.20,0:47:05.20,人物介绍,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)\pos(223.934,195.436)}{\pos(480,250)}{\fs16} {\fn微软雅黑}{\bord1\b1}洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.44,0:47:05.21,正文,,0,0,0,,她是塔斯的布蕾妮\N{\fs16}She's Brienne of Tarth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.25,0:47:07.95,正文,,0,0,0,,塞尔温・塔斯伯爵的女儿\N{\fs16}Her father is Lord Selwyn Tarth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.98,0:47:09.58,正文,,0,0,0,,听说过塔斯岛吗？\N{\fs16}Heard of Tarth?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.82,0:47:12.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我要割了你的喉咙！\N{\fs16}I'm gonna cut your throat!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.49,0:47:15.49,正文,,0,0,0,,也叫“蓝宝石之岛” 知道为什么吗？\N{\fs16}They call it the Sapphire Isle. Do you know why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.52,0:47:18.53,正文,,0,0,0,,维斯特洛的所有蓝宝石\N{\fs16}Every sapphire in Westeros{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.56,0:47:20.09,正文,,0,0,0,,都产自塔斯岛\N{\fs16}was mined on Tarth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.13,0:47:23.60,正文,,0,0,0,,蓝宝石是一种宝石\N{\fs16}Sapphires are gemstones.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.63,0:47:26.93,正文,,0,0,0,,- 蓝色的那种 - 这个我明白\N{\fs16}- The blue ones. - I know what they are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.97,0:47:30.71,正文,,0,0,0,,如果你把她送回去\N{\fs16}Lord Selwyn would pay his daughter's weight{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.74,0:47:33.44,正文,,0,0,0,,塞尔温伯爵会付给你和她一样重的蓝宝石作为赎金\N{\fs16}in sapphires if she's returned to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.48,0:47:36.71,正文,,0,0,0,,但必须是活着的\N{\fs16}But only if she's alive,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.75,0:47:39.65,正文,,0,0,0,,并且清誉无损\N{\fs16}her honor unbesmirched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.06,0:47:52.09,正文,,0,0,0,,把她带回这来\N{\fs16}Bring her back here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.16,0:47:53.53,正文,,0,0,0,,是 大人\N{\fs16}Yes, my lord.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.56,0:47:56.06,正文,,0,0,0,,- 起来 - 过来\N{\fs16}- Get up. - Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.10,0:47:58.73,正文,,0,0,0,,站起来 走过来\N{\fs16}Come on, on your feet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.97,0:48:02.17,正文,,0,0,0,,完璧\N{\fs16}Unbesmirched.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.67,0:48:05.91,正文,,0,0,0,,没破处\N{\fs16}Not defiled.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.94,0:48:08.71,正文,,0,0,0,,讲究人说讲究话哈\N{\fs16}Fancy word for a fancy man.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.81,0:48:12.45,正文,,0,0,0,,我小时候很讨厌读书\N{\fs16}I hated to read as a child,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.48,0:48:15.28,正文,,0,0,0,,但我父亲逼着我每天早上起来念书\N{\fs16}but my father forced me to study the books every morning{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.32,0:48:18.49,正文,,0,0,0,,直到我可以练剑骑马\N{\fs16}before I could practice with sword or horse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.55,0:48:21.89,正文,,0,0,0,,每天被闷在学士的屋子里两个小时\N{\fs16}Two hours every day holed up in the maester's chambers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.92,0:48:25.36,正文,,0,0,0,,我学了很多文绉绉的语言\N{\fs16}I learned a lot of fancy words.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.39,0:48:27.59,正文,,0,0,0,,我看也是\N{\fs16}I bet you did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.74,0:48:37.77,正文,,0,0,0,,你老爹\N{\fs16}Your father,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.81,0:48:40.67,正文,,0,0,0,,会付和你一般重的金子赎你回来？\N{\fs16}he'd pay your weight in gold to get you back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.18,0:48:45.11,正文,,0,0,0,,你下半辈子都会很富有的\N{\fs16}You'll be a rich man till the end of your days.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.15,0:48:47.01,正文,,0,0,0,,你的儿子们也会很富有\N{\fs16}And your sons will be rich men{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.05,0:48:49.38,正文,,0,0,0,,你的孙子们也是\N{\fs16}and their sons after them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.42,0:48:51.72,正文,,0,0,0,,封地 爵位――\N{\fs16}Lands, titles--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.75,0:48:54.02,正文,,0,0,0,,都会有的\N{\fs16}you'll have them all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.69,0:48:58.83,正文,,0,0,0,,北境赢不了这场战争的\N{\fs16}The North can't win this war.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.86,0:49:01.43,正文,,0,0,0,,你是个聪明人 你知道这点\N{\fs16}You're a smart man. You understand that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.46,0:49:03.16,正文,,0,0,0,,我们兵多将广 我们国库丰盈\N{\fs16}We have the numbers. We have the gold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.20,0:49:05.27,正文,,0,0,0,,没错 这俩你们都有\N{\fs16}Aye, you have both.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.80,0:49:09.74,正文,,0,0,0,,为了一个终将失败的目标奋勇作战\N{\fs16}Fighting bravely for a losing cause{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.77,0:49:11.61,正文,,0,0,0,,是令人钦佩的\N{\fs16}is admirable.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.64,0:49:14.31,正文,,0,0,0,,为了一个最终胜利的目标作战\N{\fs16}Fighting for a winning cause{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.34,0:49:16.84,正文,,0,0,0,,则有实打实的好处\N{\fs16}is far more rewarding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.88,0:49:19.28,正文,,0,0,0,,这倒真得承认\N{\fs16}Hard to argue with that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.55,0:49:25.52,正文,,0,0,0,,那我们敞开天窗说亮话\N{\fs16}Now that we're speaking together man to man,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.56,0:49:29.76,正文,,0,0,0,,我觉得你没必要非把我锁在树上\N{\fs16}I wonder if you need to keep me chained to this tree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.79,0:49:32.20,正文,,0,0,0,,我不是要求松绑\N{\fs16}I'm not asking to be freed from my constraints,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.23,0:49:36.03,正文,,0,0,0,,但如果我能躺着睡下\N{\fs16}but if I could sleep lying down,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.07,0:49:37.87,正文,,0,0,0,,我的背会很感激的\N{\fs16}my back would thank you for it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.90,0:49:39.94,正文,,0,0,0,,我不再像曾经那样\N{\fs16}I'm not as young{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.97,0:49:42.64,正文,,0,0,0,,年轻而有活力了\N{\fs16}and resilient as I was once.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.67,0:49:44.68,正文,,0,0,0,,我们都不小了\N{\fs16}None of us are.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.98,0:49:49.18,正文,,0,0,0,,把詹姆爵士从树上放下来\N{\fs16}Unchain Ser Jaime from the tree.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.21,0:49:51.65,正文,,0,0,0,,来吧 伙计\N{\fs16}Come on, men.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.06,0:50:00.39,正文,,0,0,0,,我觉得你可能想填填肚子？\N{\fs16}Suppose you'll be wanting something to eat.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.43,0:50:02.29,正文,,0,0,0,,实际上 我快饿死了\N{\fs16}I'm famished, actually.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.33,0:50:05.43,正文,,0,0,0,,我想火堆上还多了一只烤鹧鸪\N{\fs16}I think we've got a spare partridge on the fire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.47,0:50:08.27,正文,,0,0,0,,呃 我喜欢鹧鸪\N{\fs16}Well, I do like partridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.71,0:50:17.68,正文,,0,0,0,,把那些鸟拿过来 还有切肉刀\N{\fs16}Bring the bird over here and the carving knife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.18,0:50:23.62,正文,,0,0,0,,这能当您的餐桌吗 大人？\N{\fs16}Will this work as a table, my lord?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.65,0:50:25.52,正文,,0,0,0,,哦 好的 好的 这样感觉很――\N{\fs16}Oh, yes. Yes, this will do nic--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.55,0:50:27.65,正文,,0,0,0,,啊！\N{\fs16}ah!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.69,0:50:29.86,正文,,0,0,0,,趴上去\N{\fs16}On the stump.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.53,0:50:39.17,正文,,0,0,0,,你觉得你是这里面脑瓜子最灵光的？\N{\fs16}You think you're the smartest man there is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.90,0:50:44.27,正文,,0,0,0,,每个人都得点头哈腰\N{\fs16}That everyone alive has to bow and scrape{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.30,0:50:46.41,正文,,0,0,0,,舔你的靴子\N{\fs16}and lick your boots.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.44,0:50:48.94,正文,,0,0,0,,- 我父亲―― - 无论你遇上任何麻烦\N{\fs16}- My father-- - And if you get in any trouble,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.97,0:50:51.84,正文,,0,0,0,,只要报上你父亲的大名\N{\fs16}all you've got to do is say "my father"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.88,0:50:54.91,正文,,0,0,0,,就能拍屁股走人\N{\fs16}and that's it, all your troubles are gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.51,0:50:59.42,正文,,0,0,0,,- 不要 - 你有什么要说的吗？\N{\fs16}- Don't. - Have you got something to say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.46,0:51:06.72,正文,,0,0,0,,小心点 话可别乱说\N{\fs16}Careful. You don't want to say the wrong thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.06,0:51:12.76,正文,,0,0,0,,没你爹你屁都不是\N{\fs16}You're nothing without your daddy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.80,0:51:16.23,正文,,0,0,0,,而他恰好不在呢\N{\fs16}and your daddy ain't here.{\r}
