Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.46,0:51:40.69,正文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}男孩 山羊 跳舞的熊{\i1}\N{\fs16}Three boys, a goat, and a dancing bear
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.10,0:51:43.63,正文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}边跳边转 慢慢走向美人{\i1}\N{\fs16}They danced and spun right to the fair
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.92,0:51:47.05,正文,,0,0,0,,{\i1}她好甜 纯洁 美容{\i1}\N{\fs16}How sweet she was, so pure and fair
